## Registries
- Realms: `data/sheets/realms_registry.csv` + `rules/realms_registry.yaml`
- Front Matter Schema: `data/sheets/front_matter_schema_v1.csv`
- Sensitivity Classification: `data/sheets/sensitivity_classification_registry.csv`
