# =============================================================================
# TASK EXECUTION REQUIREMENTS
# =============================================================================

## When Making Changes
1. **Canon Check**: Verify changes align with Genesis + EOS protocols
2. **Registry Updates**: If adding/altering rules/props/tables/folders, update matching registry files in same change
3. **Layer Compliance**: Ensure changes respect 7-layer governance order
4. **Non-Destructive**: Prefer quarantine over delete, preserve lineage

## Output Requirements
- Produce changes consistent with canon above
- Include a short "Canon Check" section explaining alignment to Genesis + specific EOS rules
- Explicitly cite which canon rules you are adhering to
- If requirement is unclear, infer from Genesis/registries first
- If still ambiguous, choose safer, more conservative interpretation (no destructive actions)

